  "content_markdown": "1\n\n###  Application and Definitions\n\n1.1\n\n  1. (1) This Part applies to every function a __person__ (P) performs in relation to a _firm _(A) that is:\n     1. (a) a _CRR firm_ ;\n     2. (b) a _credit union_ ; or\n     3. (c) a _third country CRR firm_ in relation to:\n        1. (i) the activities of its establishment in the _UK_ ; or\n        2. (ii) if it does not have an establishment in the _UK_ , activities in the _UK_.\n  2. (2) This Part only applies if P:\n     1. (a) is approved under section 59 of _FSMA_ to perform a _senior management function_ in relation to A;\n     2. (b) is an _employee_ of A that should have been so approved;\n     3. (c) is an _employee_ or _director_ who is performing a function that would have been a controlled function but for [Senior Management Functions 2.3](/pra-rules/senior-management-functions#341993027e134deca39941fc85cb3e7f \"Senior Management Functions 2.3\");\n     4. (d) performs a _certification function_ in relation to A;\n     5. (e) is a _Conduct Rules non-executive director_ of A; or\n     6. (f) is a _person_ in relation to whom a notice under _section 59ZZA_ has been or could be given by the _PRA_ to an _authorised person_.\n  3. (3) [3.1](/pra-rules/conduct-rules#e49509a0167e4d67861fedff886a7428 \"3.1\") to [3.3](/pra-rules/conduct-rules#5ad723607dbf430caa934461741e2a1c \"3.3\") only apply to a _person_ in (2)(a), (b), or (f).\n  4. (4) [3.4](/pra-rules/conduct-rules#b6d1dd59bf614ff986342d49d317ca8e \"3.4\") only applies to a _person_ in (2)(a), (b), (e) or (f).\n\n*Effective: 31/12/2020*\n\n1.2\n\nIn this Part, the following definitions shall apply:\n\n_director_\n\nmeans, in relation to a _firm_ , a _person_ who is a member of the board of directors of the _firm_ or, if there is no such board, the equivalent body responsible for the management of the _firm_.\n\n_employee_\n\nhas the meaning given in [Certification ](/pra-rules/certification#2055307212bd44c7906411081040b335 \"Certification 1.3\")[1.2](/pra-rules/certification#4004e9bf25644a3c98160b704fee54dd \"1.2\").\n\n_senior management function_\n\nmeans either a _PRA senior management function_ or an _FCA designated senior management function_.\n\n*Effective: 07/11/2017*\n\n2\n\n###  Individual Conduct Rules\n\n2.1\n\n**Individual Conduct Rule 1** : You must act with integrity.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n2.2\n\n**Individual Conduct Rule 2:** You must act with due skill, care and diligence.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n2.3\n\n**Individual Conduct Rule 3** : You must be open and co-operative with the _FCA_ , the _PRA_ and other regulators.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n3\n\n###  Senior Manager Conduct Rules\n\n3.1\n\n**Senior Manager Conduct Rule 1:** You must take reasonable steps to ensure that the business of the _firm_ for which you are responsible is controlled effectively.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n3.2\n\n**Senior Manager Conduct Rule 2** : You must take reasonable steps to ensure that the business of the _firm_ for which you are responsible complies with the relevant requirements and standards of the _regulatory system_.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n3.3\n\n**Senior Manager Conduct Rule 3** : You must take reasonable steps to ensure that any delegation of your responsibilities is to an appropriate _person_ and that you oversee the discharge of the delegated responsibility effectively.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n3.4\n\n**Senior Manager Conduct Rule 4:** You must disclose appropriately any information of which the _FCA_ or _PRA_ would reasonably expect notice.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"col9\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"part-content\">\n\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"f6b0b9e080f941b3b838035c0c541186\" id=\"5eb2f8547f8c4c39b44c0be1229c2470\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication and Definitions\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"11e749e3280e43d68ca82172d2ed297f\" id=\"6ef32b89c84142539b3130b20b3b6fc8\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) This Part applies to every function a <em><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em></em> (P) performs in relation to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a> </em>(A) that is:</li>\n<ol>\n<li>(a) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52112\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c73af3cf1d2447f1ab892ff7d8f3a231\" title=\"CRR firm\">CRR firm</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(b) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52110\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-b44a7177579342ff87047c3ce2d561b6\" title=\"credit union\">credit union</a></em>; or</li>\n<li>(c) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66829\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-6223a754ecda4ccbb521f93965c95ec1\" title=\"third country CRR firm\">third country CRR firm</a></em> in relation to:</li>\n<ol>\n<li>(i) the activities of its establishment in the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52122\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-f7844a8cbb824a52a26c043e3f6b584e\" title=\"UK\">UK</a></em>; or</li>\n<li>(ii) if it does not have an establishment in the <em style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52122\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-f7844a8cbb824a52a26c043e3f6b584e\" title=\"UK\">UK</a></em>, activities in the <em style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52122\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-f7844a8cbb824a52a26c043e3f6b584e\" title=\"UK\">UK</a></em>.</li>\n</ol>\n</ol>\n<li>(2) This Part only applies if P:</li>\n<ol>\n<li>(a) is approved under section 59 of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em> to perform a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66852\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7e02825707f94364bbbbe5cebee8284e\" title=\"senior management function\">senior management function</a></em> in relation to A;</li>\n<li>(b) is an <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66850\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-956e8d7ec6684157b81ec2bc6e4d37a6\" title=\"employee\">employee</a></em> of A that should have been so approved;</li>\n<li>(c) is an <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66850\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-956e8d7ec6684157b81ec2bc6e4d37a6\" title=\"employee\">employee</a></em> or <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52144\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-003127b8ca1d48fcb0612a82af1e31c7\" title=\"director\">director</a></em> who is performing a function that would have been a controlled function but for <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/senior-management-functions#341993027e134deca39941fc85cb3e7f\" title=\"Senior Management Functions 2.3\">Senior Management Functions 2.3</a>;</li>\n<li>(d) performs a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52563\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-82074f76e19f49a5b684450294320fee\" title=\"certification function\">certification function</a></em> in relation to A;</li>\n<li>(e) is a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"78125\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-fe19114715c34e35bd07e96896ecdb72\" title=\"Conduct Rules non-executive director\">Conduct Rules non-executive director</a></em> of A; or</li>\n<li>(f) is a <em style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> in relation to whom a notice under <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"98241\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d4cdfb2b435742b7a2f0aef1d189bb13\" title=\"section 59ZZA\">section 59ZZA</a></em> has been or could be given by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> to an <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53233\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-2165460176e44a0b9cad0f898b857fb1\" title=\"authorised person\">authorised person</a></em>.</li>\n</ol>\n<li>(3) <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/conduct-rules#e49509a0167e4d67861fedff886a7428\" title=\"3.1\">3.1</a> to <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/conduct-rules#5ad723607dbf430caa934461741e2a1c\" title=\"3.3\">3.3</a> only apply to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> in (2)(a), (b), or (f).</li>\n<li>(4) <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/conduct-rules#b6d1dd59bf614ff986342d49d317ca8e\" title=\"3.4\">3.4</a> only applies to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> in (2)(a), (b), (e) or (f).</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/conduct-rules/03-07-2017#6ef32b89c84142539b3130b20b3b6fc8\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.1 before 31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"dcece05b8d80451493b0c96cae379b00\" id=\"07b4aae51e0f469bbcdd03ff3a6daa64\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>In this Part, the following definitions shall apply:</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"78128\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-857df2dfb361420188d7820d08511473\" title=\"director\">director</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means, in relation to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>, a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> who is a member of the board of directors of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> or, if there is no such board, the equivalent body responsible for the management of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>.</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66850\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-956e8d7ec6684157b81ec2bc6e4d37a6\" title=\"employee\">employee</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">has the meaning given in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/certification#2055307212bd44c7906411081040b335\" title=\"Certification 1.3\">Certification </a><a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/certification#4004e9bf25644a3c98160b704fee54dd\" title=\"1.2\">1.2</a>.</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66852\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7e02825707f94364bbbbe5cebee8284e\" title=\"senior management function\">senior management function</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means either a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52568\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-1a0e61be7ef34efba8c7c001ca8c26d3\" title=\"PRA senior management function\">PRA senior management function</a></em> or an <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66851\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-e26cb1aba5b84f108df8ef7ac24c421b\" title=\"FCA designated senior management function\">FCA designated senior management function</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/11/2017\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/conduct-rules/03-07-2017#07b4aae51e0f469bbcdd03ff3a6daa64\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.2 before 07/11/2017\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"819083d9f8d7437e863a2cc49d171cea\" id=\"44164990c8874802bee6a9d70289e779\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tIndividual Conduct Rules\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"754c686cf2154c0a86e564aad327f254\" id=\"adf4d0c4a14b4fd181759ec68f1ecc38\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><strong>Individual Conduct Rule 1</strong>: You must act with integrity.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"27e527bb24344baaac4113a0dddf74bd\" id=\"7d0d0e63eb9b4a4783e6df52fd3ac4b1\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><strong>Individual Conduct Rule 2:</strong> You must act with due skill, care and diligence.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"8eded5ee5d6b4bb2a9fbfeeca3481007\" id=\"4e114094c4d74b81b59e44a9d29e1617\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><strong>Individual Conduct Rule 3</strong>: You must be open and co-operative with the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52718\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a6adfc5faca24b3186f3f7bee3c6db22\" title=\"FCA\">FCA</a></em>, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> and other regulators.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"90e8103d29894854a1db33d2cdac60cb\" id=\"81e911d6d2a34228a519bb684e01107f\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t3\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tSenior Manager Conduct Rules\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"7aa43f2a3bc946dbaf1d0f5691474a61\" id=\"e49509a0167e4d67861fedff886a7428\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><strong>Senior Manager Conduct Rule 1:</strong> You must take reasonable steps to ensure that the business of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> for which you are responsible is controlled effectively.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"4fcb96e388844fcea1e428efde35d4e7\" id=\"f3feb96ffae54ff39ee7efc31f6e4aa9\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><strong>Senior Manager Conduct Rule 2</strong>: You must take reasonable steps to ensure that the business of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> for which you are responsible complies with the relevant requirements and standards of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52098\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8b88ef3d27fa45aeba6c11a8df1a92ac\" title=\"regulatory system\">regulatory system</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"e1495a85f1fe40658a0f2b3a0f6dfdba\" id=\"5ad723607dbf430caa934461741e2a1c\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><strong>Senior Manager Conduct Rule 3</strong>: You must take reasonable steps to ensure that any delegation of your responsibilities is to an appropriate <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52720\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8908b89166da420a9af9860d5df57ab9\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> and that you oversee the discharge of the delegated responsibility effectively.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"5dd2363ebbbd4c5f8c35857d6d36848f\" id=\"b6d1dd59bf614ff986342d49d317ca8e\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.4\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><strong>Senior Manager Conduct Rule 4: </strong>You must disclose appropriately any information of which the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52718\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a6adfc5faca24b3186f3f7bee3c6db22\" title=\"FCA\">FCA</a></em> or <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> would reasonably expect notice.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>",
  "raw_sha256": "f9ae6c34069816133737143294a20e7c5f6f68a56155fb6affc4846a41af3e44",
  "canonical_json_path": null
}